reviews.text: Good tasting Korean restaurant that has authentic flavours. It is a little more pricey than other options but still within a reasonable price limit (under $450 per person (Feb 2019) for a set BBQ dinner). The restaurant ambience on the 27th floor is more on the 'fine dining side' and classy with an intimate layout design that makes you feel somewhat more peaceful conducive for easier conversations between friends than other more bustling and hectic Korean restaurants. The views over Victoria harbour are beautiful, so if you are lucky enough to be seated by the window, you have nice sweeping views of the harbour making the whole experience that bit more enjoyable. Service can be a little slow at times, but with persistent calling, once you get the staff's attention, they are quick to get you what you need. Overall, really nice authentic Korean flavours and nice high quality ambience. Highly Recommended!
Food quality and taste good.specilly meat is very good. also Nice view to victoria sea

침사추이 27층에 위치해 있어서 전망 좋은 곳에서 식사를 할수 있는 곳입니다 멀리 홍콩섬 까지 볼수있어서 분위기로는 최고라고 할수 있습니다 

하지만 전망 말고 음식이 나왔을때는 전혀 다른 이야기 시작 됩니다 

반찬 이야기는 안 하겠습니다 설렁탕을 시켰는데 미지근한 설렁탕이 도착했습니다 

그리고 소금 간 까지 미리 되어있는 그런 설렁탕이 였습니다 

아주 하얀 기름기는 전혀 없고 너무 맑고 깨끗하고 하얀 짠맛 밖에는 없는 

인스턴트 설렁탕도 아닌 커피 프림 넣고 만든 모조 설렁탕이 틀림 없어 보였습니다 

이렇게 좋은 곳에서 장사를 하면서 숟가락 젓가락도 좋은걸 쓰는 사장님이 홍콩 달러 151HK 짜리 설렁탕에 이렇게 음식에 장난을 치는 사람이 있나 싶네요 

여기 가실분 들이라면 한번더 생각해 보고 가세요 라고 말씀 드리고 싶습니다
We love this restaurant! Great service and food. lovely place.

望海，景觀一樓; 食物不貴，百多元一客
環境絕對一流, 食物水準都很高, 地方舒適

reviews.text: Isquare  Is a nice shopping mall it has really call art work in front of it. It's really busy has a lot of nice shops that are all open past 10:00 p.m. It's in a convenient location from the Subway. Has some good restaurants in it. And the movie theater

It's a modern and great design shopping center and close to my hotel. I went here for a lunch and found Mark & Spencer on the ground floor and shopped a bit here. Overall, it's a nice shopping center.
Good for shopping (M&S clothing and food hall, marketplace), kids-r-us and other kid brands, very good cinema, linked to TST MTR train station
Visited the EyeLounge.  Very nice location with breath taking views of the city! Good drinks and very nice restaurant and cuisine.
High end shopping mall in Kowloon. Big brands.
